TEXT FULL: Job Summary

We are looking for a skilled and passionate Android Developer to design and build high-quality mobile applications for the Android platform. The candidate should have a strong understanding of mobile development, clean coding practices, and the ability to create user-friendly and performance-optimized apps.

🔧 Key Responsibilities
Develop and maintain Android applications using Kotlin or Java
Collaborate with UI/UX designers, backend developers, and product teams
Integrate REST APIs and third-party services
Debug and fix bugs to improve application performance
Ensure application scalability, security, and responsiveness
Write clean, efficient, and reusable code
Perform testing and optimize apps for performance
Stay updated with the latest Android development trends
🎯 Required Skills & Qualifications
Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, IT, or related field
Strong knowledge of Kotlin and/or Java
Familiarity with Android Studio & Android SDK
Understanding of XML layouts and UI design principles
Knowledge of REST APIs and JSON
Experience with databases (SQLite / Room)
Understanding of MVVM/MVC architecture
Familiarity with Git or version control tools
Strong problem-solving and debugging skills
⭐ Preferred Skills (Good to Have)
Experience with Firebase (Authentication, Firestore, Notifications)
Knowledge of Material Design guidelines
Experience publishing apps on the Play Store
Familiarity with testing tools like JUnit, Espresso
Basic understanding of CI/CD pipelines
