TEXT FULL: 📱 Android Developer — Job Description

🧾 Overview

We are looking for a skilled Android Developer to design, build, and maintain high-performance mobile applications. The ideal candidate should have a strong understanding of Android development, modern UI frameworks, and scalable architecture.

⸻

🚀 Key Responsibilities

* Develop and maintain Android applications using Kotlin / Java
* Build modern UI using Jetpack Compose or XML
* Integrate RESTful APIs and third-party libraries
* Collaborate with designers and backend developers
* Optimize app performance, responsiveness, and scalability
* Debug and fix bugs, improve code quality
* Write clean, maintainable, and testable code
* Follow best practices like MVVM architecture

⸻

🛠️ Required Skills

* Strong knowledge of Android SDK
* Experience with Android Studio
* Understanding of MVVM architecture
* Experience with APIs using Retrofit / Volley
* Knowledge of local databases (Room / SQLite)
* Familiarity with Git and version control

⸻

⭐ Preferred Qualifications

* Experience with dependency injection (Hilt / Dagger)
* Knowledge of Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Push Notifications)
* Understanding of Material Design principles
* Experience publishing apps on Google Play Store

⸻

🎯 Soft Skills

* Problem-solving mindset
* Strong communication and teamwork
* Attention to detail
* Ability to learn and adapt quickly
